{
  "id": "rules_glossary/t/timing",
  "lookup_group": "rules_glossary",
  "lookup_id": "timing",
  "title": "Timing",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Many card effects resolve at a specific time (for example, \u201cwhen you perform a test\u201d). Any effects that don\u2019t specify a timing are either ongoing effects that are always in effect, or effects that you can choose to use during any Ranger\u2019s"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "turn"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/t/turns",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/turns"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Effects that specify a timing will do so relative to a step in the rules (or sometimes another game effect) using one of the following words:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Before:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The effect"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "resolves"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/resolve",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/resolve"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "immediately before you begin the specified step."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The effect"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "resolves"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/resolve",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/resolve"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "during the specified step. This usually modifies the entire step in some way or triggers at a specific time within the step itself. Read that step\u2019s rules for more clarification."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "After:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The effect"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "resolves"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/resolve",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/resolve"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "immediately after all effects of the specified step have been resolved."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "If multiple effects would resolve during the same timing window, you can choose the order in which they resolve (see the"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Delightful Rule"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/d/the_delightful_rule",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/D/delightful_rule"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Triggered Effect Timing"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "link": {
            "id": null,
            "anchor": "triggered-effect-timing",
            "url": "#triggered-effect-timing"
          }
        }
      ],
      "anchor": "triggered-effect-timing"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Effects that can be triggered by you (such as"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "exhaust"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/e/exhaust",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/E/exhaust"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "abilities on your"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ranger cards"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/ranger_cards",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/ranger_cards"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "or the discard effect on Dayhowler) that do not have a timing specified can only be used at the beginning or end of your or another Ranger\u2019s"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "turn"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/t/turns",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/turns"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". Thus, they cannot be used while a test is being performed or while another card\u2019s effect is in the process of"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "resolving"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/resolve",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/resolve"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "items": [],
  "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/T/timing"
}